Name: Bifra Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Lesser Bifra Rune, Level 2 Spell Slot
Description: This rune symbolizes the bridge between realms, a path from the divine to mortalkind, allowing those who channel it to tap into the power of translocation.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACEPrismatic BoltSPACEAs an action, you summon forth a bolt of chromatic light and launch it at a target within DISTANCE50-75DISTANCE feet of you. Make a ranged spell attack against a target within range. On a hit, the target takes DAMAGE2-4DAMAGEd10 radiant damage and are teleported to an unoccupied location of your choice within DAMAGE30-45DAMAGE feet of their original location. A creature teleported into the air as a result of this effect falls at a rate of DAMAGE15-20DAMAGE feet per round until it lands, taking no falling damage and can land on its feet.SPACESPACEYou may invoke this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest. This rune occupies 3 runic attunement slots. Requires Wisdom 15 or greater to attune for a creature who did not craft the rune.
